sentences.english: There is a power point for shaver in the bathroom.
sentences.chinese: 浴室里有供电动剃须刀用的电源插座。

sentences.english: No ballasts, cooling fans or effectors needed. LED lights use standard light bulb sockets.
sentences.chinese: 不需要驱动器或冷却风扇标准的电源插座接头。

sentences.english: Power sockets for benches will be shown in the relative plan view.
sentences.chinese: 工作台上的电源插座在相关侧面图上标示。

sentences.english: The fire has been blamed on a space heater or an overloaded power strip.
sentences.chinese: 这场火灾是由于取暖器或者是电源插座过载所致。

sentences.english: The reefer containers should be stacked where there are power sockets.
sentences.chinese: 冷藏箱应当堆码在有电源插座的部位。

sentences.english: Connect the power cable to the EVM power jack on the board.
sentences.chinese: 连接电源线的EVM板上的电源插座。

sentences.english: Intuitively, the total flow of a network is the rate at which water comes out of the outlet .
sentences.chinese: 直观，总流量的网络的速度水出来的电源插座。

sentences.english: It’s a thrill in many ways similar to the one you get by putting your fingers in a power outlet.
sentences.chinese: 这是一种像是把手放在电源插座得到的兴奋。

sentences.english: Reput the plug in the socket and open the machine.
sentences.chinese: 重新将插头插入电源插座并开启本产品。

sentences.english: I've also got a clever plug which you can adapt to fit any socket anywhere.
sentences.chinese: 我还有一个万能插头，可以插到任何一种电源插座上。
